---
// The Tondela name story — green text open on the cream About page.
---

<section class='name-story'>
  <div class='name-story-header'>
    <h2>A name rooted in Tondela</h2>
    <p>
      Our name carries the memory of a local signal: foresight, courage, and
      preparation at the exact moment they matter most.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class='name-story-body'>
    <p>
      Our name is rooted in Tondela, the town that will host our facilities,
      and in an ancient local legend from the Serra do Caramulo.
    </p>
    <p>
      During the battles between Christians and Moors, a brave Christian woman
      is said to have stood watch from a hilltop, looking for approaching
      enemies. When danger appeared, she sounded her horn, her tone, alerting
      the soldiers below and giving her people time to prepare.
    </p>
    <p>
      Her foresight helped turn the tide. In honor of her courage, the
      settlement became known as Tondela, from tom dela, her tone.
    </p>
    <p>
      Like the legendary signal of Tondela, Siren stands for vigilance,
      resilience, and strategic action. We bring that same spirit to building a
      thoughtful, future-ready cannabis company in Portugal.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .name-story {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: clamp(96px, 10vw, 168px) 24px 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: clamp(32px, 3.5vw, 52px);
  }
  .name-story-header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: clamp(20px, 2vw, 28px);
  }
  .name-story-header h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 3.2vw, 52px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--color-stromboli);
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .name-story-header p {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 30em;
    font-size: clamp(17px, 1.45vw, 22px);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-aquamarine);
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .name-story-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: clamp(16px, 1.6vw, 22px);
    max-width: 38em;
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.3vw, 19px);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-te-papa-green);
    /* centered like the rest of the page — a ragged left-aligned block
       reads as off-balance inside this centered composition */
    text-align: center;
  }
  .name-story-body p {
    margin: 0;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
</style>
